{"tid":1284050,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論]ONEPIECE 海賊王 第948話 漫畫情報 下週休刊5","createTime":"2019-07-04T04:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T10:20:17.000Z","uid":130563,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"586279c011ed5cd256046e311e802baa7e9c7e95","tid":1284050,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:11:30.000Z","msg":"海賊王948話 河童河松登場<br />\n<br />\n為了不讓大鬧的路飛把事情搞大，犯人們上前控制住了路飛<br />\n為了給犯人們希望，為了讓犯人們放開路飛，河松收下了鐐銬的鑰匙和他的愛刀，越獄。<br />\n阿菊和雷藏都已亮明身份，豹吾郎（此處存疑，應該是凱多的某個手下？）由此確信豹叔也是正牌豹叔。<br />\n阿菊要在他報告給凱多之前讓他閉嘴。<br />\n圖透信息：阿菊承認自己是男性，但他說他的心是女性的心&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n下週休刊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bWVE6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bWVE6M.jpg&h=5bacf770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5grZnj7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5grZnj7.png&h=afddb54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>生命卡資訊：</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1u4tn4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1u4tn4.jpg&h=52014131&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nJACK：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">已確定為魚人，鞍帶石斑魚魚人！！</span></strong><br />\n&bull;船隻 猛獁象號<br />\n&bull;年齡 28歲<br />\n&bull;身高 830cm<br />\n&bull;喜歡 象肉排<br />\n&bull;果實 象象果實古代種 Model:猛獁<br />\n<br />\nJACK係魚人，所以跌落海可以呼吸死唔去！！<br />\n年齡係28歲明顯係BUG，佢依家28咁20年前打和之國佢咪得8歲，on9<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AHo5cUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAHo5cUk.jpg&h=e2e9f319&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<strong>SBS資訊：</strong><br />\n只選取有涉及到故事設定的問答！<br />\n顯示更多會有金鋼棒！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fac2c95575277945909c5a67373a578f69c921f","tid":1284050,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"咁多料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class